# Groupomania
RÃ©po du P7 - Groupomania

STACK USED :

BACK-END

Node.js
MySQL
Sequelize
Xampp && phpMyAdmin

FRONT-END

Vue.js
Vuetify

HOW TO START THE PROJECT

1) Clone the repository

2) Launch Xampp, start both Apache and MySQL servers

3) Create a database called GROUPOMANIA - command : DATABASE CREATE GROUPOMANIA

4) Make sure you are connected to the database : -u root -p   database name : GROUPOMANIA

- You can double check the database information for the backend inside the back\config\config.json file

5) Import the groupomania.SQL file into phpMyAdmin

6) Launch the back-end server by typing "npm install" then "nodemon server" in your command terminal with CD : GroupoRepo\Groupomania\back

7) Launch the front-end server by typing "npm install" then "npm run serve" in your command terminal with CD : GroupoRepo\Groupomania\front\groupomania

8) If Vue doesn't automatically launch the application, open your browser and go to http://localhost:8080